">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%C6%A1n-nh%C3%A2n/poem-gwthNnmbNO7SIrGYPgLYKA">Tặng Vương sơn nhân - 贈王山人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-di-ch%E1%BB%A9c-th%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BB%A5c-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem-NJvolbIcDjypA5I_hCVmCw">Thái tử Trương xá nhân di chức thành nhục đoạn - 太子張舍人遺織成褥段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ti%E1%BB%83u-nhung-3/poem-bpr_uOvYC71QFSE2Z5fj2Q">Tiểu nhung 3 - 小戎 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
